content: Is this text good and can you give me feedbacks : This landscape is very stunning. It’s gorgeous because there are a lot of vibrant colors. Also, the mountains in the back are towering, high and there’s snow on the mountain, but especially at the bottom of it. Furthermore, the mountains are rocky. Moreover, there’s a man sitting on the wooden stairs watching the view. In addition, there’s ten kayaks on the water, one at the right of the man, and there’s a very small dock at the left of the man. Besides, the sky is beautiful, it’s a light blue with clouds. Finally, there’s a forest of trees at the bottom of the mountain.
